4px] px-3 py-2 text-[13px] font-medium transition-colors lg:text-sm text-brand-slate hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/news\">News</a><a class=\"rounded-[4px] px-3 py-2 text-[13px] font-medium transition-colors lg:text-sm text-brand-slate hover:bg-slate-50 hover:text-brand-blue\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></nav><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white text-brand-slate shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-slate-300 hover:text-brand-blue md:hidden\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-nav\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg><span class=\"sr-only\">Toggle menu</span></button></div></header><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-glacier text-brand-slate\"><section class=\"relative h-[100vh] min-h-[100vh] max-h-[100vh] w-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 origin-center will-change-transform\"><img alt=\"Mountain river valley — hydropower setting placeholder\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHydro1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-[1] bg-gradient-to-r from-black/60 to-transparent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-[100vh]\"><div class=\"flex min-h-0 h-full flex-col\"><div class=\"flex min-h-0 flex-1 flex-col justify-center px-4 pb-44 pt-28 md:px-8 md:pb-40 md:pt-32 lg:pl-14 lg:pr-10\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"flex items-stretch gap-5 md:gap-6\"><div class=\"w-[2px] shrink-0 self-stretch rounded-full bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><h1 class=\"text-left font-heading text-5xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl\"><span class=\"inline-block pr-[0.2em] last:pr-0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\">Precision</span><span class=\"inline-block pr-[0.2em] last:pr-0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\">hydropower</span><span class=\"inline-block pr-[0.2em] last:pr-0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\">for</span><span class=\"inline-block pr-[0.2em] last:pr-0\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)\">Nepal</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-brand-cyan\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">Alpine energy · Nepal</p><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-left text-base leading-relaxed text-white/90 md:text-lg md:leading-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\">Unitech Hydropower Company Limited develops run-of-river hydropower with modern technology, environmental responsibility, and transparent delivery—supporting Nepal&#x27;s renewable energy future and local communities in project areas.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-[4px] border border-transparent bg-brand-blue px-7 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-white shadow-sm transition-[border-color,box-shadow] hover:border-brand-cyan hover:shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(0,210,255,0.25)] focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-4 focus-visible:outline-brand-cyan md:text-sm\" href=\"/projects\">View projects<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-[4px] border border-white/35 bg-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-[border-color,box-shadow,background-color] hover:border-brand-cyan/60 hover:bg-white/15 hover:shadow-[0_0_0_1px_rgba(0,210,255,0.22)] md:text-sm\" href=\"/about#investment-profile\">Investment profile</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-30 border-t border-white/15 backdrop-blur-lg bg-brand-blue/80 py-6\" aria-labelledby=\"technical-status-heading\"><h2 id=\"technical-status-heading\" class=\"sr-only\">Technical status</h2><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-[1440px] flex-col items-stretch justify-center px-8 md:flex-row md:px-20 divide-y divide-white/15 md:divide-x md:divide-y-0 md:divide-white/20\"><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center py-5 text-center md:px-6 md:py-0\"><p class=\"font-heading text-3xl font-bold tabular-nums tracking-tight text-glacier\">0.0<span class=\"text-brand-cyan\"> MW</span></p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/75\">Operational</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col items-center py-5 text-center md:px-6 md:py-0\"><p class=\"font-heading text-3xl font-bold tabular-nums tracking-tight text-glacier\">0<span class=\"text-brand-cyan\"> MW</span></p><p class=\"mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/75\">In pipeline</p><p class=\"mt-2 inline-flex max-w-[14rem] items-center justify-center rounded-[4px] px-2 py-1 text-[11px] leading-snug bg-brand-blue/80 text-white/70\">Middle Iwa Khola — feasibility stage</p></div></div></section></div></section><section class=\"border-b border-brand-slate/10 bg-slate-50 py-24 md:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-8 md:px-20\"><div class=\"grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr] lg:items-center lg:gap-20\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"flex items-stretch gap-4\"><span class=\"w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">About us</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 max-w-none font-heading text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-brand-blue lg:text-5xl\">A Decade of<!-- --> <span class=\"whitespace-nowrap\">Engineering Excellence</span>.</h2></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-6 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-lg md:leading-8\"><p>Unitech Hydropower Company Limited develops run-of-river hydropower with modern technology, environmental responsibility, and transparent delivery.</p><p>The company transitioned from private to public limited status to support growth, transparency, and broader stakeholder participation.</p><p><a class=\"font-semibold text-brand-blue underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" href=\"/about\">Learn more</a></p></div><div class=\"mt-10 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white px-4 py-4 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar-days h-4 w-4 text-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 18h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 18h.01\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Est.</p></div><p class=\"mt-2 font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-blue\">2014</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white px-4 py-4 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-landmark h-4 w-4 text-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M11.12 2.198a2 2 0 0 1 1.76.006l7.866 3.847c.476.233.31.949-.22.949H3.474c-.53 0-.695-.716-.22-.949z\"></path><path d=\"M14 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M18 18v-7\"></path><path d=\"M3 22h18\"></path><path d=\"M6 18v-7\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Public Ltd</p></div><p class=\"mt-2 font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-blue\">2023</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white px-4 py-4 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-slate/55\">Location</p></div><div class=\"mt-2 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-map-pin h-4 w-4 text-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><p class=\"font-heading text-sm font-bold text-brand-blue\">Taplejung &amp; Panchthar</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"relative h-full w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/60 bg-white shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/5\"><div class=\"relative h-full min-h-[420px] w-full lg:min-h-[620px]\"><img alt=\"Hydropower site placeholder — project environment\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1466611653911-95081537e5b7%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D2000%26q%3D80&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-b border-brand-slate/10 bg-glacier-mist pt-24 pb-24 md:pt-24 md:pb-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-12 md:px-20\"><div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-8 w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">Leadership</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-heading text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-brand-blue lg:text-5xl\">Chairman&#x27;s vision</h2></div></div><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-lg\">From company disclosures — integrity, accountability, and innovation as we scale from private to public company.</p></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-stretch md:gap-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><figure class=\"flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/80 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"flex min-h-[280px] flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-slate/10 to-brand-blue/[0.06] p-10\"><div class=\"flex h-24 w-24 items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-dashed border-brand-slate/20 text-brand-slate/35\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-round h-12 w-12\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"5\"></circle><path d=\"M20 21a8 8 0 0 0-16 0\"></path></svg></div><p class=\"text-center text-xs text-brand-slate/55\">Professional portrait placeholder — Anoj Khadka</p></div><figcaption class=\"border-t border-brand-slate/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-4 text-center\"><span class=\"font-heading text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-blue\">Anoj Khadka</span><span class=\"mt-0.5 block text-xs font-medium text-brand-slate/70\">Chairman</span></figcaption></figure><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center border-l-0 border-brand-cyan/70 py-2 md:border-l-4 md:pl-10\"><blockquote class=\"space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/90 md:text-lg md:leading-8\"><p class=\"font-heading text-lg font-medium italic leading-relaxed text-brand-blue md:text-xl\">“It gives me great pleasure to welcome you to Unitech Hydropower Company Limited. Since our establishment, we have remained committed to contributing to Nepal&#x27;s growing energy needs through the sustainable development of hydropower resources.”                </p><p>Our transition from a <strong>Private Limited</strong> to a<!-- --> <strong>Public Limited</strong> company reflects our dedication to <strong>growth, transparency</strong>, and<!-- --> <strong>broader stakeholder participation</strong>. We are guided by <strong>integrity, accountability, and innovation</strong>— building reliable projects that create sustainable value.</p></blockquote><p class=\"mt-6 text-sm text-brand-slate/70\">Paraphrased from the Chairman&#x27;s message and themes recorded in <span class=\"font-medium text-brand-slate\">company-context.md</span>.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"border-t border-slate-200/60 bg-white/40 py-24 backdrop-blur-sm md:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-12 md:px-20\"><div><div class=\"max-w-2xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-1 h-8 w-[2px] shrink-0 bg-brand-cyan\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-cyan\">Projects</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 font-heading text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-brand-blue lg:text-5xl\">Portfolio at a glance</h2></div></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85 md:text-lg\">Operating asset and development pipeline — full technical sheets live on a single projects page.</p></div><div class=\"mt-14 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2\"><article class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-[4px] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/90 shadow-sm backdrop-blur-sm\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[16/10] border-b border-slate-100\"><img alt=\"Upper Phawa Khola placeholder\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover object-center\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 40vw, 100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1621905251189-08b45d6a269e%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1621905251189-08b45d6a269e%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1621905251189-08b45d6a269e%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1621905251189-08b45d6a269e%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1621905251189-08b45d6a269e%3Fauto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop%26w%3D1600%26q%3D80&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/